item.title: HOW DO I MAKE MYSELF ADMIN (TESTSCAPE) and u are admin if tell!
item.dc:creator: @frugoo_scape frugoo scape
item.description:
@frugoo_scape wrote:

lol fine but…
For some answers
use http://frugooscape.net/forums
use the forums you get a good answer to all private servers there

The answer is you will have to add your user name under the administrators.txt which is located in the data folder. You could also do this which i recommend go into your characters folder and click on your user name. It will be a text file. Edit the part that says your rights. Change the character-rights = 0 part to character-rights = 3 . Thats it. Go to my site give me some bandwidth on it. http://frugooscape.net plz
oooo… also while in game just do ::mod 3 try that first
